headline: Bernstein SocGen Group Reaffirms its Outperform Rating on EQT Corporation (EQT) with a $72 Price Target
summary: With a strong profitability outlook, EQT Corporation (NYSE:EQT) secures a spot on our list of the 14 Stocks That Will Double in the Next 5 Years.
